[2023/12/06 09:09:52] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-video'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/06 09:58:32] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories

                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url

                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories

                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory

                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/06 10:18:06] SQL Query: SELECT url FROM categories WHERE name_category LIKE '%audio%' AND status = '1'
[2023/12/06 10:18:06] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-video'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/06 10:20:50] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'televisores'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            FROM categories

                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c

                                        )

                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/07 08:30:58] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-sonido'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-video'
                                            UNION

                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url

                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-video'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory

                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories

                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'audio-y-video'
                                            UNION

                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )

                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/08 10:51:51] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'televisores'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

[2023/12/08 10:56:31] SQL Query:   WITH RECURSIVE category_path AS (
                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'celulares'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory
                                        )
                                        SELECT url
                                        FROM category_path
                                        ORDER BY id_category

                                            SELECT id_category, fatherCategory, url
                                            FROM categories
                                            WHERE url = 'celulares'
                                            UNION
                                            SELECT c.id_category, c.fatherCategory, c.url
                                            FROM categories c
                                            JOIN category_path cp ON c.id_category = cp.fatherCategory

                                        ORDER BY id_category

                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '40') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category
